---
title: Cheesy Garlic & Herb Beef Quesadillas with Creamy Pesto Dressing & Tomato Salsa
description: These cheesy beef quesadillas cook all at once in the oven — perfect for getting dinner on the table with minimal fuss. Add bold
garlic-herb flavours you know and love, plus a bright tomato salsa and creamy pesto dressing for dipping and these will quickly
be your new favourite meal.
